# API Authentication

## JWT

- Config: `Jwt` section in `appsettings.json` (`Secret`, `Issuer`, `Audience`, `ExpirationMinutes`)
- Service: `JwtTokenService` implements `IJwtTokenService`
- Middleware: `AddJwtBearer` in `ServiceCollectionExtensions`

## AuthController

| Endpoint | Auth | Notes |
|----------|------|-------|
| `POST /api/auth/login` | Anonymous | Returns `AuthResponse` |
| `POST /api/auth/register` | Anonymous | Gated by `Auth:AllowRegistration` |
| `GET /api/auth/me` | `[Authorize]` | Returns `UserResponse` |

```csharp
// ✅ GOOD — anonymous login
[AllowAnonymous]
[HttpPost("login")]
public async Task<ActionResult<AuthResponse>> Login(LoginRequest request)

// ✅ GOOD — protected CRUD base
[Authorize]
public abstract class BaseController<T>
```

## Passwords

`PasswordHasher<User>` for hash/verify. Never return `PasswordHash` in DTOs.

## Claims

Token includes `sub` (user id). `Me()` resolves user from `sub` or `NameIdentifier`.

## Registration

Respect `AuthOptions.AllowRegistration`; validate email + password min 8 chars.
